{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"a709ade5-e1ce-448b-92cf-55ac67b10515","content":"The template has the **required fields** (`identity`, `name`, `shortName`, `author`, `tags`), but there are a few gaps before publishing:\n\n**Missing / Recommended:**\n| Field | Why |\n|---|---|\n| `$schema` | Enables editor validation (`http://json.schemastore.org/template`) |\n| `groupIdentity` | Required for clean install/update of NuGet template packs (e.g. `MyCompany.WebApi.CSharp`) |\n| `preferNameDirectory` | Should be `true` for project templates so `dotnet new mywebapi -n Foo` creates a `Foo/` directory |\n\n**Looks good:**\n- `sourceName`, `classifications`, `symbols` with valid choices — all correct.\n- `defaultValue: \"net9.0\"` matches a defined choice. ✓\n\n**Verdict:** Not quite ready. At minimum, add `groupIdentity` — without it, updating the template via NuGet can cause duplicate installs. Adding `$schema` and `preferNameDirectory` is also strongly recommended.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"eb6f16c0-3e71-4885-b80e-a1635580057b","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me review this template.json for NuGet publishing readiness. I need to check for required and recommended fields.\n\nIssues I can see:\n\n1. **Missing `$schema`** — Not strictly required, but highly recommended for validation and editor support. The standard value is `http://json.schemastore.org/template`.\n\n2. **Missing `groupIdentity`** — Recommended for NuGet packages, especially if you plan to have multiple related templates.\n\n3. **Missing `precedence`** — Useful when multiple versions of a template might be installed.\n\n4. **Missing `preferNameDirectory`** — Common for project templates.\n   \nThe core fields like identity, name, shortName, author, classifications, tags, and symbols are all present. The main gap is the missing `$schema` property, and for NuGet publishing you'll also need either a `.nuspec` file or a `.csproj` configured for packing.","outputTokens":747,"requestId":"C80F:1A6A:684422A:70A4790:6A03CCF4"},"id":"e0099084-0b75-42ea-98c1-5cfd0eb34fcf","timestamp":"2026-05-13T00:59:48.652Z","parentId":"f00802b4-d733-4dcc-8005-c3921da3a81e"}
